      "review_title": "Great.",
      "review_description": "This game is really well made, typically most fan games use the unity player model and make a quick 5 minute map with nothing to do and it looks garbage (no hate to any fan games) but this one is different, there’s multiple gamemodes to choose from including a shop, and some bundles that are really well made, and for a cheap price you can buy mods! There’s a lot more coming in the future updates, this game also has URP and baked lighting making the game look so amazing, and even better than most popular fan games, so that’s all I have to say, have fun!",
